{"id": 923, "genre": 1000, "title": "中产阶级的「健身营养餐」里都包含什么东西？", "description": "人是铁，范儿是钢，一天不装憋得慌。对于中产阶级这个可爱的群体，我们充满了爱意。好奇心研究所会不定期推出紧跟时代节奏的“中产阶级装腔指南”，和大家一起分享研究生活的心得。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 6607, "comment_count": 29, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703181349nAl1kcGPh2NFV69e.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-04-13T01:00:33Z", "questions": [{"id": 811, "title": "中产阶级的「健身营养餐」里都包含什么东西？", "content": "中产阶级的「健身营养餐」里都包含什么东西？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 65082, "content": "水煮鸡胸肉", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183240WA7D6hBq0tEc9XdV.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 65086, "content": "吃下去后会觉得“鸡胸肉原来也没这么难吃”的西兰花/胡萝卜丁", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183226e3st8cCmxYVw6jv7.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 65093, "content": "大约吃四份才能吃饱的分量", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183234tSVxTnclys6Qwjzo.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 65094, "content": "索然无味的脱脂牛奶/番茄汁/胡萝卜汁", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183240a21YzSUQOXFM3NDc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 65096, "content": "柚子/牛油果等低卡路里低GI值（血糖生成指数）的水果", "image": "img/option/option/20160703181313Eng1lxr4IYKzP3VF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 65098, "content": "一个为自己的蛋黄将被遗弃而默默悲伤的煮鸡蛋", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183241pAZqTQEWVlSeJ7sK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 65100, "content": "干燥到让人唾液分泌失调的各种全麦制品", "image": "img/option/option/201607021827464bpCRHN8haGPWXmS.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 65101, "content": "可以补充一点杏仁/核桃/夏威夷果等坚果", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183245aL8ekpfyPFtYNUx3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}